snippet.textDisplay:
Guys! I love these series (and secretly hope that sometime you will have something from Bulgaria), but what I didn't know is that you are flatearthers!

In the Falkland Islands round Link hit close to New Caledonia and Rhett hit Norway. You gave it to Rhett, but Link was closer! Remember, the Earth is not flat, but rather a globe. So when Link hit NC, measured to the left he is further, but measured to the right he is closer.

Anyway, I love the show. Thank you for being part of my daily routine. :)
